    to prove: (x + y)^SUC n = rsum (k=0..(SUC n)) C(SUC n,k)x^((SUC n)-k)y^k
    or (x + y) ** n = rsum (GENLIST (\k. ##(binomial n k) * x ** (n - k) * y ** k) (SUC n)) ==>
