   Base case: rsum (GENLIST (\j. f j * x ** j) 0) ** m =
              rsum (GENLIST (\j. (f j * x ** j) ** m) 0)
      Note 0 < m                      by PRIME_POS
        rsum (GENLIST (\j. f j * x ** j) 0) ** m
      = rsum [] ** m                  by GENLIST
      = #0 ** m                       by ring_sum_nil
      = #0                            by ring_zero_exp, 0 < m.
      = rsum []                       by ring_sum_nil
      = rsum (GENLIST (\j. (f j * x ** j) ** m) 0)   by GENLIST
